<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4776712>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pleurosira indica LM. Valves showing the size diminution series. Scale bar = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4776712/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4776714>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pleurosira indica SEM. A. External view of the valve showing the irregular areolae across the face. B. External view of the valve with 3 ocelli. C&D. Internal view of the valve showing the ocelli appear as depressions at the valve face and mantle junction. E. External girdle view shows the areolae extend onto the mantle. F. External view of the ocelli. G.Internal view of the valve shows the different folding nature of the rimoportulae with areolae. H. Internal view of the view shows the c-shaped depression around the rimportula. Scale bars: Figs. A, B, C, E: 10 µm; Fig. D: 5 µm; Fig. F: 2 µm; Figs. G, H: 1µm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4776714/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

